WEBVTT

00:11.911 --> 00:14.311
Somebody here is watching them.

00:14.354 --> 00:17.357
They just look creepy.

00:17.359 --> 00:19.095
I've been physically touch.

00:19.097 --> 00:21.868
Things like touching.
Ooh.

00:21.870 --> 00:24.544
They're cutting apart people
with swords.

00:24.546 --> 00:26.847
I just want a safe spot
for my family.

00:26.849 --> 00:28.349
I don't want my kids
experiencing

00:28.351 --> 00:29.717
anything that I have.

00:29.719 --> 00:33.456
They have their sights set
on the children here.

00:34.592 --> 00:36.397
It's really bad in here.

00:36.399 --> 00:38.566
My name is Amy Allan.

00:39.402 --> 00:41.604
Something is not right.

00:41.606 --> 00:42.740
I see dead people.

00:42.742 --> 00:44.978
This person might have been
a serial killer.

00:44.980 --> 00:46.815
I speak to dead people.

00:46.817 --> 00:48.550
You get those chills.

00:48.552 --> 00:49.918
And they speak to me.

00:49.920 --> 00:52.456
He is darkness.
He is evil.

00:52.458 --> 00:55.327
But there's only one way to know
if my findings are real.

00:55.329 --> 00:57.129
I think she broke her neck.

00:57.131 --> 00:58.500
I rely on my partner.

00:58.502 --> 00:59.770
I'm Steve DiSchiavi.

00:59.772 --> 01:02.974
I'm a retired New York City
homicide detective.

01:02.976 --> 01:04.309
You telling me the truth?

01:04.311 --> 01:07.413
And I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:07.415 --> 01:09.049
I think the devil is down here.

01:09.051 --> 01:10.551
It's my job to reveal them.

01:10.553 --> 01:11.719
Who the hell would do this?

01:11.721 --> 01:14.155
But Steve and I never speak...

01:14.157 --> 01:16.125
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:16.127 --> 01:17.493
...until the very end.

01:17.495 --> 01:18.862
Who's he looking to kill?

01:18.864 --> 01:20.831
We uncover if it's safe
for you to stay...

01:20.833 --> 01:23.136
You need to get out of here
right now.

01:23.138 --> 01:24.305
Or time to get out.

01:24.307 --> 01:27.044
It was like endless darkness.

